========================================
2. New Features
========================================

- hash:
  . Added MurmurHash3 with streaming support. The following variants are implemented

    - murmur3a, 32-bit hash
    - murmur3c, 128-bit hash for x86
    - murmur3f, 128-bit hash for x64

